.DESCRIPTION
	This script, if used properly, will allow you to deploy a simple install of vRA 6.2 in roughly 40 minutes.
	Take a look at the variables that need to be set.

	Assumptions for this script:
	The IAAS VM's computer name matches the VM Name
	The IAAS VM's Administrator password is VMware1!
	The IAAS "Set-Execution Policy" has been changed from restricted to Unrestricted or bypass
	The IAAS Machine has internet access (if not, refer to notes of how to use without internet)
	This is NOT a distributed install
	If you meet the above criteria, please proceed
#>

# ---------- USER CONFIGURATION -----------#
